{"title":"西财烟火觅食记 | 秋","uid":"a92b5d34203faa6d9f41960d55b5dfe1","slug":"推文17","date":"2021-12-08T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:56:33.077Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文17.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005020466.png","content":"<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005020466.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005020466\"></p>\n<p>人间忽晚，山河已秋。</p>\n<p>踩着满地银杏，走进西财的秋。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005026020.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005026020\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005030273.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005030273\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005039713.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005039713\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005042897.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005042897\"></p>\n<p>「秋天来了」的意思是</p>\n<p>街边卖糖炒栗子的小店开始排起长队</p>\n<p>月色一日比一日清素</p>\n<p>雨声从热闹变得沉寂</p>\n<p>人们个个神色清醒，心思澄净</p>\n<p>日子忽然缓慢而悠长</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005059630.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005059630\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005103521.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005103521\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005108284.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005108284\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005111891.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005111891\"></p>\n<p>有趣的人生，一半是山川湖海，一半是烟火日常 。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005125301.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005125301\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005131673.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005131673\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005136178.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005136178\"></p>\n<p>快门是时光的暂停键。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005142463.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005142463\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005146199.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005146199\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005150924.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005150924\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005157648.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005157648\"></p>\n<p>晴秋上午，随便走走，不一定要快乐</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005206499.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005206499\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005211470.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005211470\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005216059.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005216059\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005220257.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005220257\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005225665.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005225665\"></p>\n<p>所有的美好都值得等待</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005234075.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005234075\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005237775.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005237775\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005242811.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005242811\"></p>\n<p>藏在生活里的治愈时光</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005250904.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005250904\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005258097.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005258097\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005304916.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005304916\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005309860.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005309860\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005314406.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005314406\"></p>\n<p>把光收进储存卡里，下雨天再拿出来看看 </p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005332153.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005332153\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005340957.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005340957\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005347155.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005347155\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005355381.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005355381\"></p>\n<p>在琐碎的生活里，也要寻找浪漫</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005404294.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005404294\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005411330.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005411330\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220304005418407.png\" alt=\"image-20220304005418407\"></p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p><p>摄｜徐小茹 陈昕仪 刘心悦 </p>\n<p>石汶鑫 赵书峥 罗雯曦 杨钰涵 周灏 </p>\n<p>排版｜李宜霏</p>\n</p>\n</details>\n","text":" 人间忽晚，山河已秋。 踩着满地银杏，走进西财的秋。 「秋天来了」的意思是 街边卖糖炒栗子的小店开始排起长队 月色一日比一日清素 雨声从热闹变得沉寂 人们个个神色清醒，心思澄净 日子忽然缓慢而悠长 有趣的人生，一半是山川湖海，一半是烟火日常 。 快门是时光的暂停键。 晴秋上午，随...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":291,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财烟火","slug":"西财烟火","count":3,"path":"api/categories/西财烟火.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"秋","slug":"